        // The parity of (x + y) changes with each diagonal move (x+1, y+1 or x-1, y-1).
        // (x+1)+(y+1) = (x+y)+2, same parity.
        // (x+1)+(y-1) = (x+y), same parity.
        // (x-1)+(y+1) = (x+y), same parity.
        // (x-1)+(y-1) = (x+y)-2, same parity.
