// Memoization table for results of solve(start_x, current_a_val)
// dp[x] stores a pair {final_y, final_x} if starting from x and taking a_x as current_a_val
// The first element of the pair is the total y accumulated from this point,
// the second element is the x value after the first pair of operations (x+a_x, y+a_x) then (x-a_x, y+a_x)
// dp[x].first = -2 indicates not computed yet.
// dp[x].first = -1 indicates infinite loop.
